@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs(v1))
    v2 = (((v0 + 0.37 * v1 + 0.54) / wp.cos(v1 + 0.84)) - (tmp * (v1 + 0.69 / v0 + 0.21)))
    v0 = (0.76 + wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.53)))
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.28 / tmp + 0.42) - (tmp + 0.19 - v1 + 0.79)) / (v2 / 0.54))
    tmp = (((v0 + 0.36 * v0 + 0.29) / tmp) / (wp.cos(v2 + 0.84) * wp.exp(tmp + 0.31)))
    v2 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
